      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 2 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 2 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六，履霜，堅冰至。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the first SIX, divided, (we see its subject) treading on hoarfrost. The strong ice will come (by and by).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
