      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二，直方大，不習无不利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, (shows the attribute of) being straight, square, and great. (Its operation), without repeated efforts, will be in every respect advantageous.</seg>
