      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三，含章，可貞。或從王事，无成有終。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, (shows its subject) keeping his excellence under restraint, but firmly maintaining it. If he should have occasion to engage in the king's service, though he will not claim the success (for himself), he will bring affairs to a good issue.</seg>
      </tuv>
